com.mousebird.maply
Class AttrDictionary

java.lang.Object
  com.mousebird.maply.AttrDictionary

public class AttrDictionary
extends java.lang.Object

The attribute dictionary is a collection of name/value pairs. We use it to store (and modify) attributes on VectorObject structures, primarily. It's analogous to the NSDictionary class on iOS, but much simpler.
